My name is Rolf Michielson. I am a financial consultant/attorney. My client has a substantial amount of money $10.5M to invest in any good business that will bring good return on investment either in your country or anywhere in the world. My client is looking for a reliable, trustworthy and competent person to partner with. If you are interested, I will like you to email me the following:
1)    BUSINESS PLAN
2)    ANNUAL RETURN ON INVESTMENT OF THE PROPOSAL
3)    BUSINESS DURATION
4)    YOUR DIRECT TELEPHONE NUMBER
My client is willing to negotiate the terms and conditions to suit your best interest. My client will fund the investment from start to finish and is willing to share profit 50-50. If you find this letter encouraging, please indicate by a return email so we can proceed at once.
Please respond directly to my direct email, whatsapp or telephone number.
EMAIL: 
rolfmichielson876@gmail.com
WHATSAPP: +44 7467-798-558
Yours truly
Rolf Michielson (Esq)
From: r***************6@gmail.com
To: jr58299@l******s.email
Time: 2023-05-01 13:30:01
SUBJECT: Re: My name is Rolf Michielson. I
Dear Sean
How are you today? I hope all is well with you. I apologize for my late
response as I have been on and off with trying to secure my clients best
interest in this joint venture partnership.
To this effect, I thank you for the interests you have shown so far to
participate in this joint partnership Investment with my good client. IMy
client is not limited to any kind of investment. Whatever investment you
have in mind that can bring good return on investment will be reviewed and
approved for execution.
In line with the above this is all that I need from you.
1) BUSINESS SUMMARY
I need you to tell me what kind of business you intend to invest in. The
business can be anywhere in the world, not limited to your country.
2) ANNUAL RETURN ON INVESTMENT
I need to know the annual return on investment. It is limited to quotations
which might be higher or lower just to have an insight. Of course, analysis
is based on hearsay prior to business execution.
3)BUSINESS DURATION
My client is willing to let you utilize this fund for a period of 10 years
if that is acceptable by you, after which we can review our joint
partnership and see if there will be amendments or not.
The moment I get your answer back, I will start the process of this
investment partnership. I will email copies of the Joint Partnership
agreement, Non-Circumvention Non-Disclosure agreement which will be drawn
between you and my client. All necessary legal documentation covering this
transaction will be emailed to you momentarily as we advance from one stage
to the other.
To this end, I would like you to send me your direct telephone number for
faster and steady communication. Once all the agreement documents are
signed. I shall proceed with the bank for the immediate transfer of the
investment funds to any account you bring forth. I attached a copy of my
international passport for your record.
I look forward to your urgent response.
Yours Truly
Rolf Michielson
